Day 52: Revert Deployment to Previous Version in Kubernetes

Date: October 17, 2025
Overview
Rolled back problematic deployments to previous versions.
Key Concepts Learned

Rollback operations
Revision history
Deployment annotations
Recovery strategies

Commands Used
bashkubectl rollout undo deployment/nginx
kubectl rollout undo deployment/nginx --to-revision=2
kubectl rollout history deployment/nginx
Challenges Faced
Tracking which revision had working configuration. Annotations became crucial!
